<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What is Easy Read?</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Easy Read is a way of presenting information that is accessible to people with learning
  disabilities. It uses short, simple sentences and clear layout. Traditional Easy Read
  production costs approximately <strong>£120 per page</strong> and takes weeks. Simply Readable
  reduces this to approximately <strong>1p per page</strong> in minutes.
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Creating an Easy Read version</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Navigate to Simply Readable</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      From the sidebar, click <strong>Simply Readable</strong>. This section handles Easy Read conversion.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Upload a document</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Upload a .docx file containing the text you want to simplify. Use a real council document
      for the best demonstration - a tenancy agreement, council tax notice, or planning letter
      works well.
    </p>
  </li>

<div class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot govuk-!-margin-top-4 govuk-!-margin-bottom-4">
  <img src="/assets/images/screenshots/simply-readable/06-readable-upload.png"
       alt="Simply Readable upload interface showing a council tax notice document ready for Easy Read conversion"
       class="ndx-walkthrough-step__image"
       loading="lazy">
  <p class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot-caption govuk-body-s">Upload a .docx file to the Simply Readable section for Easy Read conversion</p>
</div>

  <li>
    <strong>Wait for processing</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Simply Readable uses <strong>Amazon Bedrock</strong> (Claude) to process each paragraph:
    </p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>The document is split into individual paragraphs</li>
      <li>Each paragraph is sent to the AI model for simplification</li>
      <li>The AI rewrites complex language into short, clear sentences</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      This typically takes 1-3 minutes depending on document length.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Review the results</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Once complete, you'll see the original text alongside the simplified Easy Read version
      for each paragraph. Compare them to see how complex language has been transformed into
      clear, accessible text.
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

<div class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot govuk-!-margin-top-4 govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
