<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">The impact</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Swindon Borough Council's Adult Social Care team was one of the first to adopt Simply Readable.
  Previously, creating Easy Read versions of care plans cost £120 per page and took weeks.
  Now staff can generate Easy Read versions in minutes, ensuring people with learning disabilities
  can understand their own care plans independently.
</p>

