<details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
    <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
      Troubleshooting: Easy Read not generating
    </span>
  </summary>
  <div class="govuk-details__text">
    <p class="govuk-body">If the Easy Read version doesn't generate:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Ensure you uploaded a .docx file (other formats are not yet supported for Easy Read)</li>
      <li>Wait up to 5 minutes - Amazon Bedrock processes each paragraph individually</li>
      <li>Check the job status shows paragraphs being processed</li>
      <li>If paragraphs show "generate" status for more than 5 minutes, the Bedrock invocation may have timed out - try uploading again</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</details>

